%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift%20Deepfakes%3A%20New%20Technologies%20Have%20Long%20Been%20Weaponised%20Against%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESexually%20graphic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fmusic%2F2024%2Fjan%2F28%2Ftaylor-swift-x-searches-blocked-fake-explicit-images%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cdeepfake%E2%80%9D%20images%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20last%20week%2C%20fuelling%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20Swifties%2C%20the%20general%20public%20and%20even%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20problem%20isn%E2%80%99t%20new.%20Swift%20is%20one%20of%20many%20celebrities%20and%20public%20figures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fregmedia.co.uk%2F2019%2F10%2F08%2Fdeepfake_report.pdf%5C%22%3Emainly%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20have%20fallen%20victim%20to%20deepfake%20pornography%20in%20recent%20years.%20High-profile%20examples%20garner%20significant%20media%20attention%2C%20but%20the%20increasingly%20sophisticated%20nature%20of%20AI%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-10-24%2Fartificial-intelligence-fashion-industry-models-deepfake-porn-ai%2F102997036%5C%22%3Eanyone%20can%20now%20be%20targeted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20grave%20concerns%20about%20the%20broader%20implications%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20the%20technology%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20%3Cem%3Ecause%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20abuse.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20another%20tool%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Feven-before-deepfakes-tech-was-a-tool-of-abuse-and-control-211795%5C%22%3Eused%20to%20enact%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepfakes%20and%20other%20digitally%20manipulated%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sexually%20explicit%20deepfakes%20of%20Swift%20appeared%20on%20multiple%20social%20media%20platforms%20last%20week%2C%20including%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Instagram%2C%20Facebook%20and%20Reddit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20major%20platforms%20have%20bans%20on%20sharing%20synthetic%20and%20digitally%20manipulated%20media%20that%20cause%20harm%2C%20confusion%20or%20deception%2C%20including%20deepfake%20porn.%20This%20includes%20images%20created%20through%20simpler%20means%20such%20as%20photo-editing%20software.%20Nonetheless%2C%20one%20deepfake%20depicting%20Swift%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F29%2Fx-blocks-taylor-swift-searches-what-to-know-about-the-viral-ai-deepfakes%5C%22%3Ewas%20viewed%3C%2Fa%3E%2047%20million%20times%20over%20a%2017-hour%20period%20before%20it%20was%20removed%20from%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F14680777.2018.1447341%3Fcasa_token%3DwlgXXrQJAWAAAAAA%3AZ1aslY4q9gFZPUNqzUCzYL5wjslwF86Y0m2uHLTI9FXrHnzZ1pVVowACFTX3l2maVLTKPhYM5y8PXg%5C%22%3Elong%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20digital%20technologies%2C%20apps%20and%20services%20being%20used%20to%20facilitate%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20including%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20sexual%20assault%2C%20domestic%20or%20family%20violence%2C%20dating%20abuse%2C%20stalking%20and%20monitoring%2C%20and%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20our%20focus%20should%20also%20be%20on%20addressing%20the%20problematic%20gender%20norms%20and%20beliefs%20that%20often%20underpin%20these%20types%20of%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20deepfakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20origins%20of%20deepfakes%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20November%202017%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fbjye8a%2Freddit-fake-porn-app-daisy-ridley%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Ewhen%20a%20Reddit%20user%20called%20%E2%80%9Cdeepfakes%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20a%20forum%20and%20video-editing%20software%20that%20allowed%20users%20to%20train%20their%20computers%20to%20swap%20the%20faces%20of%20porn%20actors%20with%20the%20faces%20of%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20massive%20expansion%20of%20dedicated%20deepfake%20websites%20and%20threads%2C%20as%20well%20as%20apps%20that%20can%20create%20customised%20deepfakes%20for%20free%20or%20for%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20creating%20a%20convincing%20deepfake%20often%20required%20extensive%20time%20and%20expertise%2C%20a%20powerful%20computer%20and%20access%20to%20multiple%20images%20of%20the%20person%20being%20targeted.%20Today%2C%20almost%20anyone%20can%20make%20a%20deepfake%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20harms%20of%20deepfake%20porn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20applications%20of%20AI-generated%20imagery%20are%20harmful.%20You%20might%20have%20seen%20funny%20viral%20deepfakes%20such%20as%20the%20images%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Flifestyle%2F2023%2F03%2F27%2Fpope-francis-coat-puffy-white-ai-fake%2F%5C%22%3EPope%20Francis%20in%20a%20puffer%20jacket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Or%20if%20you%20watch%20the%20latest%20Indiana%20Jones%20film%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fharrison-ford-is-back-as-an-80-year-old-indiana-jones-and-a-40-something-indy-the-highs-and-lows-of-returning-to-iconic-roles-202357%5C%22%3EHarrison%20Ford%20%E2%80%9Cde-aged%E2%80%9D%20by%2040%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20deepfakes%20are%20often%20created%20for%20malicious%20purposes%2C%20including%20disinformation%2C%20cyberbullying%2C%20child%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20sexual%20extortion%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fai-can-now-create-fake-porn-making-revenge-porn-even-more-complicated-92267%5C%22%3Eimage-based%20sexual%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.homesecurityheroes.com%2Fstate-of-deepfakes%2F%23key-findings%5C%22%3Ereport%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20startup%20Home%20Security%20Heroes%20estimated%20there%20were%2095%2C820%20deepfake%20videos%20online%20in%202023%2C%20a%20550%25%20increase%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20deepfake%20porn%2C%20women%20in%20particular%20are%20disproportionately%20targeted.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2019%2F10%2F7%2F20902215%2Fdeepfakes-usage-youtube-2019-deeptrace-research-report%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20DeepTrace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2096%25%20of%20all%20deepfakes%20online%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fregmedia.co.uk%2F2019%2F10%2F08%2Fdeepfake_report.pdf%5C%22%3Eare%20non-consensual%20fake%20videos%20of%20women%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20are%20mostly%20(but%20not%20exclusively)%20well-known%20actors%20and%20musicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20concerning%20but%20not%20surprising.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplan-international.org%2Fpublications%2Ffree-to-be-online%2F%5C%22%3EResearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20online%20abuse%20disproportionately%20affects%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20particularly%20Indigenous%20women%2C%20women%20from%20migrant%20backgrounds%20and%20lesbian%2C%20gay%2C%20bisexual%2C%20transgender%20and%20intersex%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20figures%20in%20particular%20face%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1177%2F1329878X231225745%5C%22%3Ehigher%20rates%20of%20online%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20gender-diverse%20people.%20One%20study%20found%20celebrities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F357262069_Beautiful_victims_How_the_halo_of_attractiveness_impacts_judgments_of_celebrity_and_lay_victims_of_online_abuse%5C%22%3Eare%20attributed%20more%20blame%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20non-celebrities%20for%20the%20abuse%20they%20receive%20online%2C%20and%20this%20abuse%20is%20often%20viewed%20as%20less%20serious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20shows%20image-based%20abuse%20can%20result%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1177%2F0964663920947791%5C%22%3Esignificant%20harms%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20victims%2C%20including%20anxiety%2C%20depression%2C%20suicidal%20ideation%2C%20social%20isolation%20and%20reputational%20damage.%20For%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1177%2F1329878X231225745%5C%22%3Epublic%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20deepfakes%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20online%20abuse%20can%20similarly%20result%20in%20diminished%20career%20prospects%2C%20withdrawal%20from%20public%20life%20and%20negative%20mental%20health%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Australian%20activist%20and%20law%20reform%20campaigner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watoday.com.au%2Fnational%2Fwestern-australia%2Fperth-womans-warning-after-facebook-photo-altered-and-posted-on-porn-sites-20161013-gs1xag.html%5C%22%3ENoelle%20Martin%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20photos%20were%20taken%20from%20social%20media%20and%20superimposed%20onto%20pornographic%20images.%20Martin%20reported%20feeling%20%E2%80%9Cphysically%20sick%2C%20disgusted%2C%20angry%2C%20degraded%2C%20dehumanised%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20result.%20Digitally%20altered%20and%20deepfake%20images%20of%20Martin%20continue%20to%20circulate%20online%20without%20her%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResponding%20to%20deepfake%20porn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20can%20be%20targeted%20through%20deepfakes.%20All%20that%E2%80%99s%20needed%20is%20an%20image%20of%20someone%E2%80%99s%20face.%20Even%20professional%20work%20images%20can%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20law%20reform%20alone%20won%E2%80%99t%20solve%20this%20socio-legal%20problem%2C%20it%20can%20signal%20the%20issue%20is%20being%20taken%20seriously.%20We%20need%20laws%20specifically%20targeting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Ftaylor-swift-deepfakes-a-legal-case-from-the-singer-could-help-other-victims-of-ai-pornography-222113%5C%22%3Enon-consensual%20deepfake%20porn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Australia%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imagebasedabuse.com%2Fthe-laws-in-australia%2F%5C%22%3Eimage-based%20sexual%20abuse%20offences%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20every%20Australian%20state%20and%20territory%20except%20Tasmania%2C%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20federal%20level.%20However%2C%20only%20some%20laws%20specifically%20mention%20digitally%20altered%20images%20(including%20deepfakes).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20companies%20could%20also%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20proactively%20detect%20and%20moderate%20deepfake%20porn.%20They%20need%20to%20prioritise%20embedding%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esafety.gov.au%2Findustry%2Fsafety-by-design%5C%22%3Esafety%20by%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20approaches%20into%20their%20services%20from%20the%20outset.%20This%20could%20mean%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Edesigning%20and%20testing%20AI%20with%20potential%20misuses%20in%20mind%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eusing%20watermarks%20and%20other%20indicators%20to%20label%20content%20as%20synthetic%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%9Cnudging%E2%80%9D%20users%20to%20refrain%20from%20certain%20behaviours%20(such%20as%20using%20pop-ups%20to%20remind%20them%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20consent).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20shows%20there%20are%20gaps%20in%20public%20understanding%20of%20deepfakes%20and%20how%20to%20detect%20them.%20This%20further%20highlights%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fdeepfakes-how-to-empower-youth-to-fight-the-threat-of-misinformation-and-disinformation-221171%5C%22%3Ea%20need%20for%20digital%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20education%20on%20the%20difference%20between%20consensual%20and%20non-consensual%20uses%20of%20intimate%20images%2C%20and%20the%20harms%20of%20non-consensual%20deepfake%20porn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20and%20perha