d%20shift%20and%20is%20more%20outraged%20by%20the%20greediness%C2%A0%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20not%20having%20risen%20in%20time%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20selflessly%20Herculean%20determination%20to%20oust%20the%20ruling%20right-wing%20from%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20see%2C%20if%20the%20corporate-chummy%20%E2%80%9Cnationalist%E2%80%9D%20ruling%20party%20is%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20saddle%2C%20the%20media%20must%20never%20cease%20to%20find%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20wrong%2C%C2%A0%20whatever%20journalistic%C2%A0%20calisthenics%C2%A0%20the%20job%20may%20entail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20poor%20Trump%20has%20but%20one%20Fox%20News%20backing%20him%2C%20our%20greater%20Modi%20ji%20has%20a%20bevy%20of%20them%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20not%20often%20blameworthy%20for%20being%20out%20of%20sync%20with%20the%20content%20and%20pace%20of%20moves%20on%20the%20political%20chessboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20plain%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%20in%20Bharat%20the%20appellation%20%E2%80%9Ccorrupt%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20applies%C2%A0%20only%20to%20financial%20sleaziness%2C%20never%20to%20unethical%20political%C2%A0%20practices%20(smartly%20duplicitous%20leaders%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20are%20often%20lauded%20for%20being%20the%20true%20inheritors%20of%20Chanakya)%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20having%20had%20enough%20of%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20ministership%2C%20had%20India%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministership%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20to%20happen%2C%20he%20had%20to%20have%20a%20new%20political%20conglomeration%20foregrounding%20his%20selfless%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20elevation%2C%20by%20common%20consent%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cchairperson%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20brought%20bad%20news%20to%20Nishit%20Kumar%20in%20that%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20best%20thing%2C%20therefore%2C%20to%20the%20prospect%20of%20seeing%C2%A0%20an%20alternative%20government%20with%20Kharge%20and%20the%20Congress%20at%20the%C2%A0%20helm%C2%A0%20was%20to%20make%20as%20sure%20as%20possible%C2%A0%20that%20the%C2%A0%20current%20dispensation%20carried%20on%20with%20him%20in%20the%20familiar%20chief%20minster%E2%80%99s%20chair%20after%20taking%20yet%20another%20principled%2C%20oath%20of%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20wit%2C%20bird%20in%20hand%20is%20always%20better%20than%20two%20in%20the%20bush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20may%20be%20blamed%20for%20having%20speculated%20that%20the%20next%20Nitish%20somersault%20may%20well%20happen%20if%20and%20when%20an%20alternate%20INDIA%20government%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20record%2C%20what%20is%20there%20to%20say%20this%20could%20not%20have%20happened%2C%20given%C2%A0%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20never-ending%20creativity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20might%20the%20Congress%20have%20been%20the%20only%20component%20of%20the%20alliance%20to%20have%20such%20tribulations%20on%20their%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetter%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20Kumar%20was%20given%20full%20play%20to%20reach%20his%C2%A0%20conclusions%20than%20be%20sorry%20afterwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20that%20the%20deed%20is%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20other%20federal%C2%A0%20leaders%20of%20the%20alliance%20will%20never%20be%20applauded%20by%20the%20current%20slew%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20upright%20media%20for%20having%20stood%20their%20ground%20against%20right-wing%20sectarian%20ideology%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20at%20great%20cost%20to%20themselves%20and%20their%20political%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20truly%20their%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ever-swinging%20JD(U)%20out%20%E2%80%93%20noting%20that%20many%20of%20its%20members%20are%20as%20unhappy%20with%20what%20Nitish%20has%20done%20as%20are%20those%20outside%20the%20party%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20there%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20firm%20up%20a%20truly%20secular%20and%20people-friendly%20common%20agenda%2C%20and%20take%20it%20to%20voters%2C%20especially%20in%20Bihar%2C%20who%20can%20be%20heart-warmingly%20heard%2C%20in%20such%20programmes%20as%20News24%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMahoul%20Kya%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20express%20their%20disgust%20at%C2%A0%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20latest%20turn-over%2C%20predicting%20a%20rout%20for%20the%20BJP%2FJDU%20coalition%20come%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20require%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20to%20evidence%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20solidarity%20and%20urgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20continues%20to%20make%20mass%20public%20contact%20and%20necessary%20ideological%20groundwork%2C%20equal%2C%20if%20not%20more%20energetic%20and%20visibly%20credible%2C%20primacy%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20to%20comport%20with%20all%20remaining%20segments%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20a%20real%20electoral%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kharge%20has%20rightly%20cautioned%2C%20were%20the%20coming%C2%A0%20national%20election%20to%20be%20won%20again%20by%20the%20Modi-led%20right-wing%2C%20a%C2%A0%20Putinesque%20order%20may%20well%20come%20to%20be%20a%20reality%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20leads%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20should%20the%20Rahul-led%20Yatra%20fail%20to%20become%20a%20cutting-edge%20instrument%20in%20furthering%20the%20electoral%20prospects%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20next%20election%20could%20make%20its%20heroic%20efforts%20redundant%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%C2%A0%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Congress%20wants%20to%20use%20the%20current%20campaign%20to%20obtain%20numero%20uno%20status%20as%20a%20party%2C%20it%20might%20need%20to%20rethink%20that%20objective%20for%20now%2C%20and%20yield%20to%20the%20more%20pressing%C2%A0%20task%20of%20uncomplainingly%20leaving%