of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20before%20it%20is%20adjourned%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20P.D.T.%20Achary%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20has%20never%20been%20a%20situation%20barring%20the%20present%20instance%2C%20where%20there%20has%20been%20no%20deputy%20speaker%20for%20the%20entire%20tenure%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20quite%20unlikely%20that%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20will%20be%20chosen%20by%20the%20house%20now.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20point%20now%20either.%20Deputy%20speaker%20is%20chosen%20along%20with%20the%20speaker%20and%20the%20practice%20has%20been%20to%20elect%20the%20speaker%20first%20and%20within%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20time%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20will%20also%20be%20elected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchary%20said%20that%20when%20it%20is%20a%20constitutionally%20mandated%20provision%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20adhered%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20is%20a%20mandatory%20provision%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20House%20has%20to%20abide%20by%20it.%20It%20is%20the%20House%20which%20has%20to%20elect%20the%20speaker%20as%20well%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker.%20The%20proposal%20comes%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20speaker%20is%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20convention%20has%20been%20that%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20will%20be%20from%20the%20opposition.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20written%20rule%2C%20sometimes%20the%20deputy%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20post%20has%20even%20been%20given%20to%20friendly%20opposition%20parties%20so%20they%20could%20have%20done%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Constitution%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F986229%2F%5C%22%3EArticle%2093%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Constitution%20states%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20needs%20to%20choose%20two%20members%20as%20the%20speaker%20and%20deputy%20speaker%20%E2%80%9Cas%20soon%20as%20may%20be%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20House%20of%20the%20People%20shall%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20may%20be%2C%20choose%20two%20members%20of%20the%20House%20to%20be%20respectively%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20thereof%20and%2C%20so%20often%20as%20the%20office%20of%20Speaker%20or%20Deputy%20Speaker%20becomes%20vacant%2C%20the%20House%20shall%20choose%20another%20member%20to%20be%20Speaker%20or%20Deputy%20Speaker%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpa.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FSTATISTICAL%2520HANDBOOK%25202023New_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%20Statistical%20Handbook%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20has%20been%20elected%20within%20a%20few%20weeks%20at%20the%20most.%20The%20longest%20it%20has%20taken%20till%20date%20to%20elect%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20was%20during%20the%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20it%20took%20270%20days%20to%20elect%20P.M.%20Sayeed%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20when%20G.M.C.%20Balayogi%20was%20the%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20just%20a%20week%20to%20go%20for%20Parliament%20to%20be%20adjourned%20sine%20dine%2C%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20the%20only%20one%20to%20have%20not%20had%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20for%20its%20entire%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Indian%20Parliament's%20Unending%20Bad%20Dream%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-parliaments-unending-bad-dream%5C%22%3EIndian%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20Unending%20Bad%20Dream%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feparlib.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F68%2F1%2FThe_Indian_Parliament__Eng.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Parliament%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20book%20authored%20by%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20T.K.%20Viswanathan%2C%20available%20on%20the%20Parliament%20Digital%20Library%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elect%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20from%20amongst%20themselves%2C%20who%20presides%20over%20the%20deliberations%20of%20the%20house%20during%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20deputy%20Speaker%20is%20vested%20with%20the%20same%20powers%20as%20the%20Speaker%20when%20presiding%20over%20a%20sitting%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20deputy%20Speaker%2C%20on%20being%20the%20member%20of%20a%20Parliamentary%20Committee%2C%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20that%20Committee.%20He%2C%20unlike%20the%20Speaker%2C%20can%20speak%20in%20the%20house%2C%20take%20part%20in%20its%20deliberations%20and%20vote%20as%20a%20member%20on%20any%20question%20before%20the%20house%2C%20but%20he%20can%20do%20so%20only%20when%20the%20Speaker%20is%20presiding.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20rules%20also%20state%20that%20the%20speaker%20nominates%20ten%20members%20to%20the%20Panel%20of%20Chairmen.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20speaker%20and%20the%20deputy%20speaker%2C%20one%20of%20them%20presides%20over%20the%20sittings%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20members%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20included%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rama%20Devi%2C%20Kirit%20P.%20Solanki%2C%20and%20Rajendra%20Agrawal%3B%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%3B%20A.%20Raja%20of%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%3B%20P.V.%20Midhun%20Reddy%20of%20the%20YSRCP%3B%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%20of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%3B%20N.K.%20Premachandran%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%3B%20and%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Undemocratic%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20not%20mandated%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20a%20parliamentary%20convention%20has%20developed%20over%20the%20years%20to%20choose%20a%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20was%20first%20started%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20who%20picked%20Sardar%20Hukum%20Singh%20of%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20to%20be%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20in%201956.%20Subsequently%2C%20deputy%20speakers%20were%20from%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20until%20G.G.%20Swell%2C%20an%20independent%20member%2C%20was%20appointed%20during%20the%20Emergency%20years.%20Thereafter%2C%20members%20from%20the%20opposition%20have%20occupied%20the%20post%2C%20a%20convention%20that%20continued%20till%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20the%20AIADMK%E2%80%99s%20M.%20Thambidurai%20was%20the%20deputy%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20opposition%20members%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20appoint%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20because%20of%20this%20very%20convention%20of%20appointing%20a%20member%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20whip%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20while%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Thambidurai%2C%20he%20belonged%20to%20the%20AIADMK%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20Thambidurai%20was%20made%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20even%20though%20the%20AIADMK%20was%20an%20NDA%20partner.%20In%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%2054%20members%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20opposition%20party.%20While%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20single%20largest%20opposition%20party%20has%20to%20be%2056%20to%20have%20a%20member%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20two%20members%20short.%20But%20that%20is%20completely%20technical.%20If%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20give%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20post%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20it%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20have%20not%20given%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20because%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20give%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20BJP%20government%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20deputy%20speaker%20post%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20and%20they%20have%20not%20followed%20parliamentary%20convention%20in%20both%2016th%20and%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20constitutional%20posts%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20that%20is%20why%20it%20was%20not%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%2C%20TMC%20MP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20that%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%E2%80%9D%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20had%20many%20firsts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Our%20Expectations%20from%20Indian%20Parliament%20and%20Their%20Fa%C3%A7ade%3A%20Observers%E2%80%99%20Notes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Four-expectations-from-indian-parliament-and-their-facade-observers-notes%5C%22%3EOur%20Expectations%20from%20Indian%20Parliament%20and%20Their%20Fa%C3%A7ade%3A%20Observers%E2%80%99%20Notes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20winter%20session%2C%20in%20a%20first%2C%20a%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3E146%20MPs%20were%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20firsts%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20out%20of%20which%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20is%20so%20marked.%20There%20is%20the%20explanation%20from%20the%20government%20side%20that%20the%20numbers%20in%20the%20opposition%20benches%20weren%E2%80%99t%20appropriate.%20But%20definitely%20something%20could%20have%20been%20done.%20Since%20the%20provision%20of%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20is%20there%20in%20the%20Constitution%20and%20we%20have%20been%20having%20one%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20prudent%20for%20the%20government%20to%20look%20at%20it%20more%20seriously%20and%20have%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20because%20that%20is%20the%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20undemocratic%20that%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20nearing%20completion%20without%20this%20constitutional%20post%20being%20filled.%20There%20might%20be%20another%20thought%20behind%20it%20to%20make%20the%20opposition%20weaker%2C%20and%20not%20giving%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsence%20of%20deputy%20speaker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%20session%20last%20year%20in%20August%2C%20when%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20skipped%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20as%20he%20was%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-rs-chair-says-wont-ask-modi-to-speak-on-manipur-ls-speaker-stays-away%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cupset%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20conduct%20of%20opposition%20members%2C%20members%20of%20the%20panel%20of%20chairpersons%20filled%20in%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20deputy%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20March%202020%20members%20of%20the%20panel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fom-birla-skips-ls-proceedings-what-happens-when-speaker-is-absent-8873683%2F%5C%22%3Efilled%20in%20%3C%2Fa%3Eagain%20during%20the%20Budget%20session%2C%20when%20Birla%20skipped%20the%20proceedings%20for%20two%20days%20as%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Churt%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20uproar%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20opposition%20leaders%20asking%20about%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20election%2C%20Birla%20had%20said%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20elect%20a%20person%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20House%20and%20the%20government%20to%20decide%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fhouse-govt-to-take-call-on-dy-speaker-election-ls-speaker-om-birla%2Farticleshow%2F78038922.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%20PTI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fvacant-ls-dy-speaker-post-cong-govt-destroying-established-practices-8444786%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20BJP%20sources%20that%20there%20is%20no%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20requirement%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20as%20%E2%80%9CBills%20are%20being%20passed%20and%20discussions%20being%20held%E2%80%9D.%20The%20report%20also%20cited%20BJP%20sources%20and%20said%20there%20had%20been%20some%20discussion%20in%20the%20past%20about%20choosing%20members%20from%20friendly%20parties%20like%20the%20BJD%20or%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20a%20comment%2C%20and%20this%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20comment%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20also%20reached%20court%20last%20year%2C%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fno-deputy-speaker-in-lok-sabha-some-assemblies-supreme-court-seeks-responses-of-union-states-221491%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20bench%3C%2Fa%3E%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20P.S.%20Narasimha%20and%20Justice%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%2C%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20five%20other%20assemblies%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20cited%20Articles%2093%20and%20178%2C%20reminding%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20the%20election%20of%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20is%20mandatory%20and%20sought%20responses%20on%20their%20failure%20to%20elect%20a%20deputy%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchary%20said%20that%20not%20appointing%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20goes%20against%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20say%20that%20absence%20of%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20has%20in%20no%20way%20affected%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20house%20but%20then%20why%20is%20there%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20constitution%3F%20If%20it%20was%20optional%20it%20would%20be%20made%20so%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20But%20it%20is%20mandatory%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20When%20the%20constitution%20makes%20a%20mandatory%20provision%20it%20has%20to%20be%20adhered%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706857239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02121753%2FGFGx-CPbAAAB7us-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-a-first-17th-lok-sabha-to-end-without-a-deputy-speaker%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20parliamentarians%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20did%20not%20appoint%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20as%20the%20post%20is%20conventionally%20held%20by%20a%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-a-first-17th-lok-sabha-to-end-without-a-deputy-speaker%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20First%2C%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20End%20Without%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02121753%2FGFGx-CPbAAAB7us-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20be%20the%20first%20to%20conclude%20its%20tenure%20without%20a%20deputy%20speaker%2C%20in%20a%20development%20that%20has%20been%20called%20%E2%80%9Cundemocratic%E2%80%9D%20by%20opposition%20parliamentarians%20and%20unprecedented%20by%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010-day%20interim%20budget%20session%20which%20started%20on%20January%2031%20is%20the%20last%20sitting%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20before%20it%20is%20adjourned%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20P.D.T.%20Achary%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20has%20never%20been%20a%20situation%20barring%20the%20present%20instance%2C%20where%20there%20has%20been%20no%20deputy%20speaker%20for%20the%20entire%20tenure%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20quite%20unlikely%20that%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20will%20be%20chosen%20by%20the%20house%20now.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20point%20now%20either.%20Deputy%20speaker%20is%20chosen%20along%20with%20the%20speaker%20and%20the%20practice%20has%20been%20to%20elect%20the%20speaker%20first%20and%20within%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20time%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20will%20also%20be%20elected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchary%20said%20that%20when%20it%20is%20a%20constitutionally%20mandated%20provision%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20adhered%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20is%20a%20mandatory%20provision%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20House%20has%20to%20abide%20by%20it.%20It%20is%20the%20House%20which%20has%20to%20elect%20the%20speaker%20as%20well%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker.%20The%20proposal%20comes%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20speaker%20is%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20convention%20has%20been%20that%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20will%20be%20from%20the%20opposition.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20written%20rule%2C%20sometimes%20the%20deputy%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20post%20has%20even%20been%20given%20to%20friendly%20opposition%20parties%20so%20they%20could%20have%20done%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Constitution%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F986229%2F%5C%22%3EArticle%2093%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Constitution%20states%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20needs%20to%20choose%20two%20members%20as%20the%20speaker%20and%20deputy%20speaker%20%E2%80%9Cas%20soon%20as%20may%20be%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20House%20of%20the%20People%20shall%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20may%20be%2C%20choose%20two%20members%20of%20the%20House%20to%20be%20respectively%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20thereof%20and%2C%20so%20often%20as%20the%20office%20of%20Speaker%20or%20Deputy%20Speaker%20becomes%20vacant%2C%20the%20House%20shall%20choose%20another%20member%20to%20be%20Speaker%20or%20Deputy%20Speaker%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpa.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FSTATISTICAL%2520HANDBOOK%25202023New_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%20Statistical%20Handbook%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20has%20been%20elected%20within%20a%20few%20weeks%20at%20the%20most.%20The%20longest%20it%20has%20taken%20till%20date%20to%20elect%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20was%20during%20the%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20it%20took%20270%20days%20to%20elect%20P.M.%20Sayeed%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20when%20G.M.C.%20Balayogi%20was%20the%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20just%20a%20week%20to%20go%20for%20Parliament%20to%20be%20adjourned%20sine%20dine%2C%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20the%20only%20one%20to%20have%20not%20had%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20for%20its%20entire%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Indian%20Parliament's%20Unending%20Bad%20Dream%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-parliaments-unending-bad-dream%5C%22%3EIndian%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20Unending%20Bad%20Dream%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feparlib.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F68%2F1%2FThe_Indian_Parliament__Eng.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Parliament%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20book%20authored%20by%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20T.K.%20Viswanathan%2C%20available%20on%20the%20Parliament%20Digital%20Library%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elect%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20from%20amongst%20themselves%2C%20who%20presides%20over%20the%20deliberations%20of%20the%20house%20during%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20deputy%20Speaker%20is%20vested%20with%20the%20same%20powers%20as%20the%20Speaker%20when%20presiding%20over%20a%20sitting%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20deputy%20Speaker%2C%20on%20being%20the%20member%20of%20a%20Parliamentary%20Committee%2C%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20that%20Committee.%20He%2C%20unlike%20the%20Speaker%2C%20can%20speak%20in%20the%20house%2C%20take%20part%20in%20its%20deliberations%20and%20vote%20as%20a%20member%20on%20any%20question%20before%20the%20house%2C%20but%20he%20can%20do%20so%20only%20when%20the%20Speaker%20is%20presiding.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20rules%20also%20state%20that%20the%20speaker%20nominates%20ten%20members%20to%20the%20Panel%20of%20Chairmen.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20speaker%20and%20the%20deputy%20speaker%2C%20one%20of%20them%20presides%20over%20the%20sittings%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20members%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20included%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rama%20Devi%2C%20Kirit%20P.%20Solanki%2C%20and%20Rajendra%20Agrawal%3B%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%3B%20A.%20Raja%20of%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%3B%20P.V.%20Midhun%20Reddy%20of%20the%20YSRCP%3B%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%20of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%3B%20N.K.%20Premachandran%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%3B%20and%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Undemocratic%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20not%20mandated%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20a%20parliamentary%20convention%20has%20developed%20over%20the%20years%20to%20choose%20a%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20was%20first%20started%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20who%20picked%20Sardar%20Hukum%20Singh%20of%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20to%20be%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20in%201956.%20Subsequently%2C%20deputy%20speakers%20were%20from%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20until%20G.G.%20Swell%2C%20an%20independent%20member%2C%20was%20appointed%20during%20the%20Emergency%20years.%20Thereafter%2C%20members%20from%20the%20opposition%20have%20occupied%20the%20post%2C%20a%20convention%20that%20continued%20till%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20the%20AIADMK%E2%80%99s%20M.%20Thambidurai%20was%20the%20deputy%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20opposition%20members%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20appoint%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20because%20of%20this%20very%20convention%20of%20appointing%20a%20member%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20whip%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20while%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Thambidurai%2C%20he%20belonged%20to%20the%20AIADMK%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20Thambidurai%20was%20made%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20even%20though%20the%20AIADMK%20was%20an%20NDA%20partner.%20In%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%2054%20members%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20opposition%20party.%20While%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20single%20largest%20opposition%20party%20has%20to%20be%2056%20to%20have%20a%20member%20as%20the%20deputy%20speaker%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20two%20members%20short.%20But%20that%20is%20completely%20technical.%20If%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20give%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20post%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20it%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20have%20not%20given%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20because%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20give%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20BJP%20government%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20deputy%20speaker%20post%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20and%20they%20have%20not%20followed%20parliamentary%20convention%20in%20both%2016th%20and%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20constitutional%20posts%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20opposition%20party%20that%20is%20why%20it%20was%20not%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%2C%20TMC%20MP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20that%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%E2%80%9D%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20had%20many%20firsts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Our%20Expectations%20from%20Indian%20Parliament%20and%20Their%20Fa%C3%A7ade%3A%20Observers%E2%80%99%20Notes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Four-expectations-from-indian-parliament-and-their-facade-observers-notes%5C%22%3EOur%20Expectations%20from%20Indian%20Parliament%20and%20Their%20Fa%C3%A7ade%3A%20Observers%E2%80%99%20Notes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20winter%20session%2C%20in%20a%20first%2C%20a%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3E146%20MPs%20were%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20firsts%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20out%20of%20which%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20is%20so%20marked.%20There%20is%20the%20explanation%20from%20the%20government%20side%20that%20the%20numbers%20in%20the%20opposition%20benches%20weren%E2%80%99t%20appropriate.%20But%20definitely%20something%20could%20have%20been%20done.%20Since%20the%20provision%20of%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20is%20there%20in%20the%20Constitution%20and%20we%20have%20been%20having%20one%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20prudent%20for%20the%20government%20to%20look%20at%20it%20more%20seriously%20and%20have%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20because%20that%20is%20the%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20undemocratic%20that%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20nearing%20completion%20without%20this%20constitutional%20post%20being%20filled.%20There%20might%20be%20another%20thought%20behind%20it%20to%20make%20the%20opposition%20weaker%2C%20and%20not%20giving%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsence%20of%20deputy%20speaker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%20session%20last%20year%20in%20August%2C%20when%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20skipped%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20as%20he%20was%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-rs-chair-says-wont-ask-modi-to-speak-on-manipur-ls-speaker-stays-away%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cupset%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20conduct%20of%20opposition%20members%2C%20members%20of%20the%20panel%20of%20chairpersons%20filled%20in%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20deputy%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20March%202020%20members%20of%20the%20panel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fom-birla-skips-ls-proceedings-what-happens-when-speaker-is-absent-8873683%2F%5C%22%3Efilled%20in%20%3C%2Fa%3Eagain%20during%20the%20Budget%20session%2C%20when%20Birla%20skipped%20the%20proceedings%20for%20two%20days%20as%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Churt%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20uproar%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20opposition%20leaders%20asking%20about%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20election%2C%20Birla%20had%20said%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20elect%20a%20person%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20House%20and%20the%20government%20to%20decide%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fhouse-govt-to-take-call-on-dy-speaker-election-ls-speaker-om-birla%2Farticleshow%2F78038922.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%20PTI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fvacant-ls-dy-speaker-post-cong-govt-destroying-established-practices-8444786%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20BJP%20sources%20that%20there%20is%20no%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20requirement%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20deputy%20speaker%20as%20%E2%80%9CBills%20are%20being%20passed%20and%20discussions%20being%20held%E2%80%9D.%20The%20report%20also%20cited%20BJP%20sources%20and%20said%20there%20had%20been%20some%20discussion%20in%20the%20past%20about%20choosing%20members%20from%20friendly%20parties%20like%20the%20BJD%20or%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20a%20comment%2C%20and%20this%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20comment%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20also%20reached%20court%20last%20year%2C%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%