20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20judge%20also%20said%20that%20the%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20entertain%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20plea%20against%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20summons%20to%20him%20on%20the%20same%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20challenging%20the%20ED%20arrest.%20When%20he%20filed%20a%20similar%20petition%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20his%20counsel%20Sibal%20undertook%20that%20he%20would%20withdraw%20the%20high%20court%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Sibal%20and%20Singhvi%20attempted%20to%20convince%20the%20court%20that%20it%20has%20concurrent%20jurisdiction%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20in%20its%20report%20that%20despite%20%E2%80%9Cfervent%20appeals%E2%80%9D%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjudges%20remained%20unswayed%E2%80%9D%20and%20spoke%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20Article%20226%20remedy%20for%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20also%20did%20not%20stipulate%20a%20timeframe%20for%20the%20high%20court%20even%20upon%20request.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20going%20to%20control%20the%20high%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20remarked%20that%20a%20common%20man%20would%20never%20get%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20separate%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20trying%20to%20topple%20this%20government%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20fact%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706854751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02115438%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-hemant-soren-jharkhand-high-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20M.M.%20Sundresh%2C%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20asked%20the%20Jharkhand%20CM's%20co