sassinated%20Saunders%2C%20an%20act%20for%20which%20he%20was%20hanged.%20Lajpat%20Rai%20is%20almost%20always%20remembered%20as%20a%20great%20leader%20who%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20for%20the%20nation%E2%80%A6%20But%20Lajpat%20Rai%20is%20also%20known%20in%20another%20avatar%3A%20as%20an%20ideological%20ancestor%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20ideology%20first%20elaborated%20properly%20by%20Vinayak%20Damodar%20Savarkar%20in%20his%201923%20tract%20%3Cem%3EHindutva%3A%20Who%20is%20a%20Hindu%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20Proponents%20of%20Hindutva%20today%20make%20a%20clear%20and%20assertive%20claim%20on%20Lajpat%20Rai%20as%20one%20of%20their%20own%E2%80%A6.%20Interestingly%2C%20this%20Hindu%20nationalist%20claim%20on%20Lajpat%20Rai%20as%20their%20icon%20is%20confirmed%20by%20dominant%20interpretations%20of%20the%20man%20in%20historical%20scholarship%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20325px)%2085vw%2C%20325px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02111306%2F9780670094073-3.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22325%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02111306%2F9780670094073-3.jpeg%20431w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02111306%2F9780670094073-3-199x300.jpeg%20199w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695330%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22490%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVanya%20Vaidehi%20Bhargav%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EBeing%20Hindu%2C%20Being%20Indian%3A%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20Ideas%20of%20Nationhood%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPenguin%20Random%20House%20India%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20interpretation%20of%20Lajpat%20Rai%20ends%20up%20leaving%20out%20much%20nuance%20and%20complexity%E2%80%A6%20The%20absence%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20study%20of%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20nationalist%20thought%20has%20facilitated%20his%20evaluation%20as%20a%20predecessor%20of%20Savarkar%E2%80%A6%20This%20book%20undertakes%20precisely%20such%20an%20examination%20of%20the%20nationalist%20thought%20of%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%A6%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20contests%20dominant%20interpretations%20that%20iron%20out%20the%20intellectual%20shifts%2C%20fluidity%20and%20complexity%20in%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20thought%20to%20evaluate%20him%20as%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20precursor%2C%20either%20sharing%20deep%20ideological%20affinities%20with%20Hindutva%20or%20even%20representing%20some%20nascent%2C%20softer%20variety%20of%20it%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20this%20book%E2%80%99s%20central%20aims%20is%20to%20show%20that%20even%20when%20Lajpat%20Rai%20articulated%20his%20most%20robust%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20first%20decade%20of%20the%20twentieth%20century%2C%20it%20diverged%20from%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20in%20important%20ways.%20Lajpat%20Rai%20viewed%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20as%20separate%20%E2%80%98nationalities%E2%80%99%20and%20converged%20with%20Savarkarite%20Hindutva%20when%20he%20took%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20culture%E2%80%99%20to%20constitute%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation.%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20also%20shared%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20view%20that%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20was%20crystallized%20in%20Hindu%20historical%20resistance%20against%20the%20foreign%20Muslim%20enemy.%20Yet%2C%20even%20then%2C%20Lajpat%20Rai%20stood%20at%20quite%20a%20distance%20from%20Hindutva.%20He%20envisioned%20a%20friction-ridden%20yet%20cooperative%20relationship%20between%20the%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20%E2%80%98nationalities%E2%80%99%20within%20a%20common%20state.%20His%20ability%20to%20see%20the%20Muslim%20nation%20existing%20robustly%20alongside%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20was%20vastly%20different%20from%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20demand%20that%20to%20become%20part%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation%2C%20Indian%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20must%20abandon%20all%20marks%20of%20their%20religion%20and%20culture%20and%20assimilate%20into%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20culture%E2%80%99.%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalism%20lacked%20Savarkarite%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20desire%20for%20Hindu%20cultural%20supremacy%20and%20its%20aversion%20to%20religio-cultural%20diversity%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Notable%20People%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Touched%20During%20His%20Lifetime%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbhagat-singh-jawaharlal-nehru-bal-gangadhar-sarojini-naidu%5C%22%3EThe%20Notable%20People%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Touched%20During%20His%20Lifetime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%201915%2C%20when%20Lajpat%20Rai%20committed%20himself%20to%20using%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98nation%E2%80%99%20to%20signify%20only%20one%20large%20cultural%20community%20which%20needed%20to%20express%20itself%20in%20an%20independent%20state%2C%20he%20elaborated%20a%20richly%20textured%20nationalist%20narrative%20firmly%20grounded%20in%20the%20notion%20that%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20constituted%20a%20single%20%E2%80%98Indian%20nation%E2%80%99.%20He%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20prove%20their%20common%20Indian%20nationhood%20by%20constructing%20for%20them%20a%20shared%20hybrid%20ancestry%20and%20a%20pluralist%20culture%2C%20and%20by%20rewriting%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Muslim%E2%80%99%20history.%20By%20unearthing%20this%20narrative%2C%20my%20research%20shows%20that%20whether%20or%20not%20Hindutva%20further%20developed%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20national%E2%80%99%20ideas%20articulated%20earlier%20by%20Lajpat%20Rai%2C%20his%20own%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20gave%20way%20to%20a%20rich%2C%20distinctive%20Indian%20nationalist%20narrative.%20Indeed%2C%20his%20new%20conceptualization%20of%20nationhood%20led%20him%20to%20support%20the%20Pan-Islamic%20Khilafat%20movement%20led%20by%20Gandhi%20and%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Indian%20Muslim%20leadership%20from%201919%20to%201921.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20may%20be%20assumed%20about%20a%20supposed%20forefather%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20during%20the%20Khilafat%20movement%2C%20rather%20than%20expressing%20a%20Hindu%20nationalism%20fearful%20of%20Muslim%20religiosity%20and%20suspicious%20about%20their%20%E2%80%98extraterritorial%20loyalties%E2%80%99%2C%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20nationalism%20urged%20Hindus%20to%20respect%20Muslim%20religious%20sentiments%20and%20sympathies%20towards%20the%20Ottoman%20caliphate%20and%20the%20Muslim%20world.%20It%20also%20strove%20to%20promote%20trust%20between%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20In%20proffering%20reasons%20for%20why%20Hindus%20must%20support%20this%20%E2%80%98Muslim%E2%80%99%20cause%2C%20Lajpat%20Rai%2C%20much%20like%20Gandhi%2C%20stressed%20that%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%93Muslim%20unity%E2%80%99%20was%20crucial%20for%20both%20Indian%20national%20identity%20and%20Indian%20self-government.%20As%20we%20can%20see%2C%20pigeonholing%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20entire%20thought%20as%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20obscured%20a%20historical%E2%80%93intellectual%20juncture%20when%20a%20Hindu%20political%20figure%20like%20him%20enthusiastically%20supported%20Pan-Islamism%20as%20necessary%20for%20Indian%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20book%20further%20seeks%20to%20challenge%20historical%20scholarship%20which%20assumes%20that%20when%2C%20in%20the%20chaotic%20and%20violent%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Khilafat%20movement%2C%20Lajpat%20Rai%20joined%20and%20led%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20he%20elaborated%20a%20Hindu%20%E2%80%98communalism%E2%80%99%20that%20was%20equivalent%20to%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99.%20It%20shows%20that%20in%20the%20mid-1920s%2C%20in%20response%20to%20changed%20political%20contexts%2C%20Lajpat%20Rai%20elaborated%20yet%20another%20new%20and%20distinct%20%E2%80%98Indian%E2%80%99%20nationalist%20narrative.%20The%20militant%20Hindu%20politics%20he%20sought%20to%20engineer%20through%20the%20Mahasabha%20aimed%20at%20establishing%20a%20radically%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20state%20and%20politics%E2%80%94free%20of%20all%20markers%20of%20religion%E2%80%94which%20he%20now%20considered%20a%20crucial%20precondition%20for%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20united%20Indian%20nation.%20From%20the%20more%20trust-based%20and%20other-embracing%20secular%20Indian%20nationalism%20he%20articulated%20during%20the%20Khilafat%20movement%2C%20Lajpat%20Rai%20moved%20to%20a%20more%20distrustful%20and%20hard-line%20secular%20Indian%20nationalism%20that%20was%20explicitly%20hostile%20to%20community-based%20politics.%20His%20vehement%20opposition%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20meant%20that%20a%20move%20from%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20Indian%20nationalist%20conception%20does%20not%20always%20involve%20a%20move%20towards%20a%20politics%20more%20accommodative%20towards%20Muslim%20demands.%20Even%20so%2C%20like%20his%20militant%20Hindu%20politics%2C%20his%20secular%20Indian%20nationalism%20had%20integrity%20and%20meaning.%20Grounded%20in%20moral%20and%20political%20values%2C%20it%20was%20not%20just%20a%20ploy%20to%20institute%20Hindu%20majority%20domination.%20As%20a%20Mahasabha%20leader%2C%20he%20also%20remained%20willing%20to%20relinquish%20his%20radically%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20vision%20of%20state%20and%20politics%20to%20concede%20reservations%20to%20the%20Muslim%20%E2%80%98minority%E2%80%99%20if%20this%20was%20required%20for%20Indian%20national%20unity%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Brief%20History%20of%20the%20Radically%20Different%20Nationalisms%20Vying%20To%20Shape%20the%20Indian%20Republic%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-nationalisms-brief-history%5C%22%3EA%20Brief%20History%20of%20the%20Radically%20Different%20Nationalisms%20Vying%20To%20Shape%20the%20Indian%20Republic%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20book%20argues%20against%20intellectual%20reductionism%20and%20the%20pigeonholing%20of%20all%20of%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20into%20either%20Hindutva%20or%20a%20moderate%20variety%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20or%20indeed%20secular%20Indian%20nationalism.%20Doing%20this%20has%20prevented%20us%20from%20noticing%20the%20subtleties%2C%20nuances%20and%20distinctiveness%20of%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20thought%20at%20particular%20junctures.%20They%20have%20prevented%20us%20from%20recognizing%20the%20distinctive%20texture%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20he%20regularly%20articulated%20before%201915%2C%20and%20its%20difference%20from%20Hindutva.%20They%20have%20also%20prevented%20us%20from%20noticing%20shifts%20and%20changes%20in%20his%20thought%20across%20time.%20We%20failed%20to%20heed%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20distinct%20%E2%80%98Indian%20nationalist%E2%80%99%20narratives%20during%20the%20Khilafat%20movement%20and%20even%20his%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20phase.%20The%20internal%20complexity%2C%20fluidity%20and%20dynamism%20of%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20nationalist%20thought%20make%20it%20resistant%20to%20easy%20overall%20categorization.%20If%20one%20has%20to%20make%20such%20an%20evaluation%2C%20one%20can%20only%20say%E2%80%94rather%20vaguely%E2%80%94that%20%3Cem%3Etaken%20collectively%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20distinct%20and%20internally%20complex%20narratives%20that%20Lajpat%20Rai%20articulated%20in%20his%20political%20life%2C%20remain%20an%20intellectual%20position%20distinct%20from%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20moderate%20varieties%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20official%20ideology%20of%20%E2%80%98Indian%20nationalism%E2%80%99.%20The%20important%20takeaway%20really%20is%20that%20blanket%2C%20catch-all%20categorizations%20of%20Lajpat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20nationalist%20thought%20have%20prevented%20us%20from%20properly%20understanding%20it%2C%20and%20from%20forensically%20examining%20its%