here%20is%20no%20abnormality%20in%20the%20foetus.%20It%20is%20a%20full-fledged%2C%20normal-bodied%20child.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20case%20we%20should%20entertain%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20just%20a%20question%20of%20another%20two%20weeks%20or%20so.%20Even%20the%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20child%20for%20adoption.%20The%20medical%20board%20says%20her%20life%20will%20be%20at%20risk%20in%20a%20pre-term%20pregnancy.%20We%20cannot%20permit%20it.%20All%20these%20points%20have%20been%20considered%20by%20the%20high%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20petition%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20woman%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20pregnancy%20was%20causing%20her%20mental%20trauma%20and%20depression.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20widow%20and%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20live%20with%20this%20trauma.%20This%20pregnancy%20is%20against%20her%20choice%20and%20wishes%20that%20will%20cause%20further%20trauma%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20advocate%2C%20Rahul%20Sharma%2C%20had%20said%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20held%20that%20it%20had%20to%20think%20of%20both%20the%20woman%20and%20the%20unborn%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20had%20previously%20permitted%20the%20abortion%20but%20reversed%20its%20decision%20after%20medical%20opinions%20suggested%20that%20the%20foetus%20was%20healthy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-abnormality-in-foetus-sc-turns-down-abortion-plea-of-32-week-pregnant-woman-101706688852186.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20woman%20then%20challenged%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20January%2023%20order%20which%20said%20the%20foetus%20does%20not%20show%20any%20abnormality%20and%20so%20a%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20would%20not%20be%20justified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Medical%20T