inst%20him%20for%20putting%20out%20a%20status%20on%20WhatsApp%20against%20the%20frenzy%20created%20all%20around%20on%20the%20consecration%20day.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20the%20student%20took%20a%20critical%20take%20against%20the%20celebration.%20It%20was%20a%20copied%20post%20from%20another%20fellow%20student.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20students%20had%20put%20out%20social%20media%20statuses%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20ongoing%20celebrations%20on%20the%20IIPS%20campus.%20But%20only%20one%20student%20was%20singled%20out%20and%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20say%20that%20the%20post%20was%20a%20mere%20excuse.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20said%20student%20would%20have%20become%20a%20target%20anyway.%20Many%20students%20and%20even%20the%20administration%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20student%20and%20his%20friends%E2%80%99%20endeavour%20of%20organising%20students%20against%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20celebration%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20students%2C%20who%20too%20had%20signed%20the%20letter%20sent%20to%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CIIPS%20is%20a%20multicultural%20campus%20annually%20organising%20various%20celebrations%20which%20includes%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20Dussehra%2C%20Christmas%2C%20etc%20which%20epitomises%20the%20promise%20of%20grooming%20a%20secular%20young%20generation%20who%20can%20contribute%20prosperity%20to%20a%20diversified%20nation-state%20like%20India.%20But%20the%20celebration%20of%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20a%20pure%20act%20of%20political%20agenda%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20various%20outfits%2C%20which%20can%20harm%20the%20secular%20sentiments%20of%20students%20while%20celebrating%20in%20an%20institute%20like%20IIPS%2C%20where%20such%20celebrations%20cannot%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20sought%20restrictions%20on%20celebrations%20on%20campus%20and%20said%20the%20celebration%20had%20the%20potential%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20deepening%20the%20divisions%20among%20student%20fraternity%20by%20spreading%20hate%20and%20fear%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20was%20overlooked.%20But%20after%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20those%20who%20had%20submitted%20the%20letter%20were%20bullied%20into%20writing%20an%20apology.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20concerns%20raised%20in%20the%20earlier%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20this%20time%20were%20made%20to%20apologise%20for%20hurting%20sentiments%20of%20those%20celebrating%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration.%20Both%20the%20letters%20were%20addressed%20to%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20555px)%2085vw%2C%20555px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084207%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-8.25.54-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22555%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084207%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-8.25.54-AM.jpeg%20985w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084207%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-8.25.54-AM-300x164.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22303%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20apology%20letter%20written%20by%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20students%20were%20forced%20to%20apologise%2C%20the%20right-leaning%20students%20celebrated%20the%20Ram%20temple%20ceremony%20with%20much%20fanfare.%20Life-size%20posters%20were%20put%20up%20across%20campus%20and%20saffron%20flags%20were%20hoisted%20across%20all%20hostels.%20The%20students%20allegedly%20took%20out%20processions%20late%20at%20night%2C%20even%20heckling%20Muslim%20students%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20event%2C%20the%20administration%20and%20students%E2%80%99%20body%20had%20strictly%20asked%20students%20to%20carry%20their%20ID%20cards%20and%20outsiders%20were%20not%20to%20be%20permitted.%20But%20many%20men%20from%20outside%20had%20allegedly%20entered%20the%20campus%20and%20participated%20in%20the%20day-long%20celebration%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20407px)%2085vw%2C%20407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084459%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-8.24.41-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22407%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084459%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-8.24.41-AM.jpeg%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084459%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-8.24.41-AM-263x300.jpeg%20263w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22464%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20message%20sent%20out%20by%20student%20representatives%20asking%20everyone%20to%20carry%20their%20IDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20arrest%20of%20a%20student%20from%20campus%20is%20unusual.%20Usually%2C%20the%20police%20never%20enter%20the%20space%20without%20the%20institute%20administration%E2%80%99s%20permission.%20Also%2C%20when%20there%20is%20a%20dispute%2C%20the%20complaint%20is%20made%20first%20with%20the%20institute%20before%20escalating%20it%20with%20the%20police.%20But%20here%2C%20the%20complainant%2C%20a%20second-year%20master%E2%80%99s%20student%2C%20went%20directly%20to%20Govandi%20police%20station.%20The%20student%20was%20booked%20under%20Section%20153%20(A)%20and%20295%20(A)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccreating%20enmity%20between%20religion%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20in%20the%20remand%20application%20claimed%20that%20the%20student%20had%20offended%20Hindu%20students%20with%20his%20WhatsApp%20post.%20The%20student%20was%20arrested%20and%20kept%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20two%20days.%20On%20the%20third%20day%20as%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20Arthur%20Road%20central%20jail%2C%20a%20local%20court%20granted%20him%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20is%20back%20on%20campus.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20for%20comment%20but%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20students%E2%80%99%20organisations%20like%20the%20Ambedkar%20Student%20Association%20(ASA)%20have%20been%20dismantled.%20A%20student%2C%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20association%2C%20said%20that%20soon%20after%20the%20arrest%2C%20students%20dropped%20out%20and%20their%20WhatsApp%20group%20was%20deleted.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20being%20targeted%20for%20our%20political%20understanding%20and%20assertion.%20Most%20of%20us%20come%20from%20poor%20family%20backgrounds%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20fight%20the%20right-wing%20forces.%20So%2C%20students%20just%20decided%20to%20dismantle%20the%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20student%20who%20was%20earlier%20associated%20with%20the%20ASA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706844408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084846%2FIIPS.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmumbai-student-arrested-after-asking-admin-to-curb-ram-temple-celebrations-on-campus%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2023-year-old%20Dalit%20student%20was%20one%20of%20many%20who%20had%20written%20a%20confidential%20letter%20to%20the%20institute's%20director%20and%20also%20put%20up%20a%20status%20on%20WhatsApp%20questioning%20the%20frenzy%20on%20January%2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmumbai-student-arrested-after-asking-admin-to-curb-ram-temple-celebrations-on-campus%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%