thousands%20of%20workers%20were%20complicit%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20a%20dozen%20other%20countries%20announced%20that%20they%20would%20pause%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20in%20the%20Near%20East%20(UNRWA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UN%20immediately%20fired%20those%20workers%20and%20announced%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20a%20query%20at%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20India%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20development%20partner%20of%20Palestine%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20regularly%20extended%20aid%2C%20both%20bilaterally%20and%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20have%20a%20policy%20of%20zero%20tolerance%20towards%20terrorism%2C%20and%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20we%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20at%20the%20allegations%20that%20the%20UNRWA%20staff%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20spokesperson%20also%20appended%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Cwelcome(s)%20investigations%20launched%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20this%20regard%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20Jaiswal%20omitted%20any%20reference%20to%20cutting%20funds%20to%20the%20UN%20agency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20met%20its%20annual%20contribution%20of%20%245%20million%20to%20UNRWA%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehanding%20over%20%242.5%20million%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2024%2Fsc15575.doc.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20UN%20Security%20Counc