things%2C%20then%20we%20would%20have%20achieved%20something%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20she%20studied%20abroad%20and%20was%20involved%20with%20activism%20with%20people%20of%20all%20political%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20the%20action%20of%20the%20RWA%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20message%20to%20everyone%20who%20believes%20abusing%20Hindu%20beliefs%20is%20%26quot%3Bpar%20for%20the%20course%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RWA%20has%20%26quot%3Basked%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20and%20his%20daughter%20to%20apologise%20for%20defiling%20the%20Pran%20Pratistha%20ceremony%20at%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20and%20leave%20the%20residential%20colony%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20IT%20department%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20or%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20-%20headlined%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20was%20held%20at%20the%20newly%20built%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706767440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe0l77j5o_suranya-aiyar-facebook_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-colony-over-ram-temple-i-dont-live-there-4971691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar's%20daughter%20Suranya%20Aiyar%2C%20who%20was%20asked%20to%20vacate%20%26quot%3Btheir%26quot%3B%20house%20in%20south-east%20Delhi%20over%20her%20Ram%20Temple%20post%2C%20has%20said%20that%20she%20doesn't%20even%20live%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-c