nt%20for%20both%20places.%20Janta%20Dairy%20targets%20the%20locals%20who%20have%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20shop%20since%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20time.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20repeat%20clientele.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Pistabarfi%20has%20a%20niche%20audience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Pistabarfi%20delivers%20all%20over%20India%20and%20is%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20coming%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250601%2Faarti-rastogi-bengaluru-food-startup-artinci-healthy-sugar-free-keto-friendly-gluten-free-desserts-ice-cream-brownies-cakes-hearing-disability-woman-entrepreneur-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue-added%20snacking%3C%2Fa%3E%20products%20that%20break%20the%20myth%20of%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E%20only%20being%20a%20festive%20reason.%20For%20instance%2C%20take%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekaju%20katli%20mithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20bar%2C%20a%20chocolate%20bar-shaped%20product%20that%20is%20actually%20%3Cem%3Ekaju%20katli%3C%2Fem%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20can%20keep%20it%20in%20their%20pocket%20and%20snack%20on%20it%20when%20they%20want%20to.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20what%20I%20would%20call%20%E2%80%98fusion%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20more%20like%20we%E2%80%99re%20making%20products%20that%20are%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20while%20the%20brothers%20have%20broken%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20segment%20with%20their%20unique%20cloud%20kitchen%20approach%2C%20Harshit%20minces%20no%20words%20when%20he%20says%20it%20is%20foolish%20to%20assume%20one%20could%20bring%20a%20complete%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20so%20accustomed%20to%20just%20walking%20down%20the%20road%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326173%2Forigins-of-iconic-indian-dishes-loved-across-the-world-food-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentering%20a%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20asking%20to%20taste%20the%20various%20sweets%20as%20we%20take%20our%20pick.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20emotion.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20Janta%20Dairy%20will%20always%20give%20its%20customers.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20going%20to%20change%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20watching%20his%20sons%20step%20in%2C%20Narottam%20(56)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20at%20the%20shop%20since%20I%20was%20in%20Class%2012.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20reality%20I%20know%20and%20lived%20for%20all%20these%20years.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20pull%20through%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20could%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20part%20of%20my%20identity%20and%20losing%20the%20shop%20would%20mean%20losing%20a%20part%20of%20myself.%20My%20sons%20prevented%20that%20from%20happening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20they%20have%20done%20is%20quite%20different%20from%20what%20I%20could%20have%20ever%20imagined.%20It%E2%80%99s%20unique%20and%20I%20feel%20proud%20as%20a%20father%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706621388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-04-20-at-2.26.43-PM-2_11zon-1706614438.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harshit%20and%20Tanay%20Agrawal%2C%20sons%20of%20Janta%20Dairy%E2%80%99s%20owner%20Narottam%2C%20saved%20their%20family%E2%80%99s%20mithai%20business%20in%20Mumbai%20amidst%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20They%20launched%20Pistabarfi%2C%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20that%20blends%20generational%20recipes%20which%20evoke%20the%20same%20taste%20as%20their%20grandfather's%20sweets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A